# Tag: title
#. Tag: title
#, no-c-format
msgctxt ""
msgid "Performing Initial Login"
msgstr "進行初次登入"

# Tag: para
#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgctxt ""
msgid ""
"You can now authenticate using the newly-created user and temporary password."
" Type <command>kinit <replaceable>&lt;user login&gt;</replaceable></command> "
"to log in to IPA. This will prompt you for a password and then immediately "
"request a password change."
msgstr ""
"您現在可以授權使用新建使用者與單次密碼。請輸入<command>kinit <replaceable>&lt;user login&gt;</"
"replaceable></command> 以登入 IPA。這將提示您輸入密碼，然後馬上開始進行更改密碼的程序。"

# Tag: para
#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgctxt ""
msgid ""
"You can browse the IPA man pages and help system to explore other IPA "
"commands. Please take some time to become familiar with the ways other IPA "
"objects can be created and modified."
msgstr "您可以瀏覽 IPA 的 man page 與求助系統，瞭解其它的 IPA 指令。請花一點時間，熟悉建立、修改其它 IPA 物件的方法。"

